summary: These news articles provide information regarding the operating hours of Walmart stores during New Year's Eve 2024 and New Year's Day 2025. Walmart will be open on New Year's Eve, and the specific closing times may vary depending on the location. However, most stores are expected to close at an earlier time than usual, such as 6 pm or 7 pm. On New Year's Day, Walmart stores will be open with limited hours. Some stores may open later in the morning and close earlier in the evening, while others may have reduced hours of operation. It is recommended to check with the specific Walmart store in your area for their exact New Year's Eve and New Year's Day hours to avoid any inconvenience.

summary: Notre Dame football is preparing for a pivotal College Football Playoff matchup against Georgia in the Sugar Bowl. Head coach Marcus Freeman's emphasis on self-improvement methods is shaping the team's approach. Key players to watch in the game include Notre Dame quarterback CJ Carr, who is determined to overcome an elbow injury. Georgia coach Kirby Smart anticipates a physical challenge from Notre Dame. The game will be televised on ESPN, and fans can also stream it or follow along with live updates. The outcome will have significant implications for both teams' CFP aspirations, as well as for Freeman's reputation as a coach.
